# Requirements
- Node.js v18.12 or higher required for pnpm
- Current Node.js version: v18.20.8 (LTS)
- pnpm version: v10.4.1

# Package Manager
Use pnpm instead of npm for package management
Example: pnpm install @radix-ui/react-slot

# Project Structure
- /app - Next.js app directory
- /components - Reusable UI components
- /lib - Utility functions and shared code

# Development
- Run development server: pnpm dev
- Build for production: pnpm build
- Start production server: pnpm start

# Dependencies
Key dependencies:
- @radix-ui/react-slot
- class-variance-authority
- clsx
- tailwind-merge
- date-fns
- tailwindcss
- postcss
- autoprefixer

# Styling
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling
- Custom theme variables in globals.css
- Component-specific styles in respective component files

# TypeScript
- Strict TypeScript configuration
- Component props are properly typed
- Use proper type imports from React and Next.js 